results.name: Zoom Kobe 4 Protro 'Black Mamba'

Kobe’s signature is scrawled in yellow on the lateral side of the TPU heel counter, delivering the shoe’s lone pop of color. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a matching black Phylon midsole, featuring a large-volume Zoom Air unit in forefoot for on-court responsiveness.

A bright crimson hue is executed on the scaly micro-mesh upper, secured with neon green laces and accented with a contrasting black Swoosh. A padded low-cut collar allows for a full range of motion, while a molded TPU heel counter provides rearfoot stability. The sneaker sits on a lightweight Cushlon midsole with a springy Zoom Air unit nestled in the forefoot.

Contrasting orange accents land on the interior lining, as well as the Jumpman branding hits found on the back heel and silver reflective tongue. results.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro PS 'Olive' 2024

Originally released in 2006, the legacy silhouette sports an olive suede upper with tonal molded eyelets and ventilated quarter panel netting. Orange textile lines the padded collar, matching the embroidered Jumpman logos that adorn the back heel and silver reflective tongue. A final splash of orange can be found on the speckled shark tooth detailing that enlivens the foam midsole.

results.name: Air Jordan 5 Retro GS 'Olive' 2024

The latter is marked with an orange Jumpman logo, matching the interior lining and a second Jumpman icon embroidered on the back heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via an Air-assisted polyurethane midsole, finished in an olive drab hue with orange shark tooth detailing. A translucent rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

Embroidered Jumpman branding graces the tongue, while the 13’s holographic eye adorns the lateral collar. Synthetic suede wraps the Phylon midsole, fitted with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning in the forefoot and heel, and supported by a panther paw rubber outsole underfoot.

results.name: Air Foamposite One 'Anthracite' 2023
results.story: The 2023 edition of the Nike Air Foamposite One ‘Anthracite’ brings back a colorway originally released in 2007. The monochromatic silhouette features a black molded polyurethane upper with tonal nubuck trim on the eyestay and collar. Penny’s 1 Cent logo adorns the jeweled tongue tag, sockliner and back tab. In terms of performance, the concealed Phylon midsole packs a full-length Zoom Air-sole unit for lightweight cushioning. Underfoot, a herringbone traction rubber outsole provides durable traction.

results.name: Jordan 11 Retro DMP Defining Moments (2023) (PS)
results.story: Offered in pre-school sizing, the Air Jordan 11 Retro PS ‘Gratitude / Defining Moments’ takes its design cues from the model’s OG ‘Concord’ colorway. The classic silhouette carries a white leather upper, bolstered with a black patent leather overlay and secured with laces that feed through tonal webbing eyelets. Branding elements, highlighted by a stylized ‘23’ on the back tab and a Jumpman logo on the lateral collar, shine in a metallic gold finish. The sneaker rests on a white Phylon midsole, supported underfoot by a semi-translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 11 Retro DMP Defining Moments (2023) (GS)
results.story: Crafted for big kids, he Air Jordan 11 Retro GS ‘Gratitude / Defining Moments’ features color blocking reminiscent of the iconic ‘Concord’ AJ11, highlighted by a white leather upper with tonal webbing eyelets and a contrasting black mudguard in glossy patent leather. A metallic gold Jumpman shines on the lateral collar, matching the stylized ‘23’ stamped on the back tab. The sneaker rests on a cushy white Phylon midsole, supported underfoot by a cream-tinted semi-translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 11 Retro Crib Bootie DMP Defining Moments (2023) (I)
results.story: The Air Jordan 11 Retro CB ‘Gratitude / Defining Moments’ transforms the iconic silhouette into a convenient slip-on, featuring a white leather upper secured with elastic no-tie laces and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap. The addition of a black patent leather mudguard results in a two-tone design reminiscent of the ‘Concord’ colorway, while a metallic gold Jumpman calls to mind the DMP edition from 2006. A soft foam midsole delivers lightweight cushioning for growing feet.

results.name: Jordan 11 Retro DMP Defining Moments (2023) (TD)
results.story: The Air Jordan 11 Retro TD ‘Gratitude / Defining Moments’ showcases color blocking that recalls the silhouette’s iconic ‘Concord’ colorway. Equipped with webbing eyelets and an added pull tab at the heel, the white leather upper is wrapped in a patent leather overlay in a glossy black finish. A metallic gold Jumpman shines on the lateral collar, disrupting the neutral two-tone palette. Anchoring the sneaker is a cushy white foam midsole, supported by a semi-translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 11 Retro DMP Defining Moments (2023)
results.story: The 2023 edition of the Air Jordan 11 Retro 'Gratitude / Defining Moments', also known as 'DMP', brings back a coveted colorway of the legacy model, originally paired with an Air Jordan 6 as one-half of the 'Defining Moments Pack' from 2006. Inspired by the OG 'Concord' colorway, the championship silhouette features a white tumbled leather upper with tonal webbing eyelets and a black patent leather mudguard. Metallic gold accents land on the shoe's branding elements, including an embossed Jumpman logo on the lateral ankle and a '23' stamped on the heel tab. The sneaker rides on a Phylon midsole, supported by a carbon fiber shank plate and a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 3 Retro Off Noir
results.story: The Women’s Air Jordan 3 Retro ‘Off Noir’ delivers a black nubuck upper with grey elephant print overlays at the forefoot and heel. Black perforated leather appears on the eyestay and padded collar, while molded eyelets are rendered in a contrasting off-white finish. Standard Jumpman branding decorates the tongue and back heel. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a two-tone polyurethane midsole with an exposed Air-sole unit nestled in the heel.

results.name: adidas Crazy 1 Mint (2023)
results.story: The adidas Crazy 1 ‘Mint’ presents a vibrant colorway of the shoe that Kobe Bryant wore during his first NBA championship season. A minty green hue is executed on the molded synthetic upper, featuring a reinforced toe bumper and debossed three-stripe branding on the quarter panel. Padded black mesh is utilized on the tongue and collar, while the interior lining reveals a contrasting bright orange finish. The sneaker rides on an EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro SE Craft Medium Olive
results.story: The Air Jordan 4 Retro SE ‘Craft’ in ‘Olive’ showcases a nubuck and suede upper in varying shades of drab green. Hairy suede quarter panels feature a debossed grid-like pattern, replacing the traditional midfoot netting of the original AJ4. Contrasting black accents settle on the leather support wings, molded eyelets and woven tongue tag, marked with Flight branding and a cream-hued Jumpman logo. A matching Jumpman icon decorates the back tab. The sneaker rests on a crisp white polyurethane midsole, enhanced with visible Air-sole cushioning in the heel.

results.name: Jordan 8 Retro SP SoleFly Diamond Turf
results.story: The SoleFly x Air Jordan 8 Retro ‘Diamond Turf’ celebrates the championship silhouette’s 30th anniversary with a collaborative release inspired by another signature shoe from 1993 — Deion Sanders’ Nike Air Diamond Turf. Taking key details from the AJ8 silhouette, this pair sports a nubuck upper with unique paint-brush overlays and an embroidered 23’ on the trademark cross-strap design. Borrowed from the Air Diamond Turf, red textile lines the interior, while gilded accents land on the sneaker’s ankle clasp, lace tips and mesh quarter panel. A two-tone foam midsole, enhanced with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning, delivers a comfortable ride. A SoleFly hangtag is attached, in the form of a home plate with the SF logo.

results.name: Nike Book 1 Chapter One
results.story: The Nike Book 1 ‘Chapter One’ presents the launch colorway of Devin Booker’s debut signature shoe. A tonal orange finish is applied to the upper, inspired by traditional workwear and featuring canvas quarter panels with scaly leather throughout the forefoot. ‘Book’ is spelled out on the woven tongue tag, while ‘Chapter One’ is inscribed on a pull tab inspired by a book spine. A midsole built with Cushlon 2.0 foam is wrapped in matching orange TPU sidewalls for added support. Nestled in the heel, a top-loaded Zoom Air unit provides on-court responsiveness.

results.name: Jordan 2 Retro Italy
results.story: The Air Jordan 2 Retro ‘Italy’ showcases a distinctive color scheme that nods to the shoe’s premium roots. The latter is outlined in two-tone piping in red and green, with the contrasting hues making a repeat appearance on the Nike-branded heel tab. Crimson textile lines the high-cut collar, matching the embossed Wings logo that decorates the tongue. The midfoot panel is surrounded by red and green piping, with the contrasting hues making repeat appearances on the shoe’s heel and interior lining. Branding elements include a Nike wordmark on the back tab and an embossed Wings logo on the tongue. Anchoring the sneaker is an off-white foam midsole with encapsulated Air-sole cushioning.

results.name: Jordan 2 Retro Italy (TD)

The latter hue makes a repeat appearance on the heel counter, while Fire Red accents land on the interior lining, Nike-branded back tab, and the retro Wings logo embossed on the tongue. A cushy foam midsole features an off-white finish for a vintage aesthetic.

A contrasting hit of Fir Green lands on the heel counter. Anchoring the sneaker is a vintage off-white midsole built with cushy foam.

results.story: The adidas Harden Vol. 8 'Sculpt' features a black textile upper, equipped with a stretchy sock-like cuff and a synthetic leather toe cap. Finished in Hazy Copper, a prominent EVA cage provides lateral support and containment. The teardrop-shaped frame extends into the full-length Jet Boost midsole. Underfoot, the rubber outsole utilizes a 'JH' traction pattern with a herringbone tread throughout the perimeter.

results.story: The Song for the Mute x adidas Country OG 'Grey Black' reimagines an archival '70s silhouette as part of the third capsule collection with the Australian fashion label. Updated with metallic D-ring eyelets, the grey nylon upper features durable tonal overlays in leather and suede. Black suede three-stripes, along with a discreet 'STM – 003' tag, adorn the lateral side, while white textile three-stripes grace the opposite side. The sneaker rests on a two-tone foam midsole, rendered in a classic wedge shape and supported by a grey herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Country OG Low Song for the Mute Black
results.story: Releasing as part of the third capsule collection with the Australian brand, the Song for the Mute x adidas Country OG 'Black Wonder Beige' utilizes cord laces that feed through metallic D-ring eyelets on the black nylon upper. A grey shaggy suede forefoot overlay and brown leather toe cap pair with a white hairy suede three-stripes on the lateral side, while the opposite side is marked with brown textile three-stripes. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a low-profile foam midsole, reinforced by a brown herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Country OG Low Song for the Mute Active Teal
results.story: Launching as part of the third capsule collection with the Australian fashion brand, the Song for the Mute x adidas Country OG 'Active Teal' revives an archival silhouette, created to equip athletes for the 1972 Munich Olympics. Laces feed through metallic D-ring eyelets to secure the dark teal nylon upper, fortified with grey suede overlays and a black leather toe cap. Mismatched black and white three-stripes adorn the lateral and medial side, while dual branding appears on the tongue tag and sockliner. Underfoot, a black herringbone rubber outsole wraps up the toe and heel of the full-length foam midsole.

Ivory three-stripes outlined in black trim adorn the quarter panels, while Bad Bunny's 'eye' logo appears on the back tab. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a foam midsole, rendered in an off-white finish to maintain the monochrome aesthetic.

adidas AE 1 All-Star
results.story: The adidas AE 1 'The Future' delivers a gleaming colorway of Anthony Edwards' debut signature shoe as part of adidas' 2024 NBA All-Star lineup. Built with black knit textile construction, the upper features a stretchy sock-like cuff and TPU-molded support wings in a metallic burgundy finish. Embossed three-stripe branding in lime green adds a vibrant pop of color at the back heel. The sneaker is mounted on a caged Jetboost midsole with Lightstrike cushioning.

results.name: END. x ZX 8000 'Consortium Cup - Future'
results.story: Launching as part of the 'Consortium Cup' series, the END. x adidas ZX 8000 'Future' delivers a monochrome colorway inspired by the dystopian landscapes of science fiction films. A dark tan finish is executed on the upper, featuring ripstop textile with burnished leather overlays and reflective 3M accents. Mismatched adidas and END. branding appears on each woven tongue tag and lace dubrae, while 'Future' is inscribed in cursive script on the lateral collar. The sneaker is mounted on a pre-distressed EVA midsole, reinforced by a brick-red rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas D.O.N. Issue #5 White Victory Blue Orange
results.story: The adidas D.O.N. Issue #5 'White Victory Blue Orange' showcases a streamlined, lightweight design. Donovan Mitchell's fifth signature shoe sports a breathable off-white mesh upper, fortified with tonal no-sew overlays and a suede toe cap. Both the lateral and medial side are accented with blue three-stripes that extend into the Lightstrike midsole, fitted with an orange-hued TPU shank for midfoot stability. Underfoot, a herringbone-traction gum rubber outsole provides superior grip.

results.name: adidas Crazy 8 1998 All-Star Game (2024)
results.story: The 2024 edition of the adidas Crazy 8 '1998 All Star Game' brings back a classic colorway from Kobe Bryant's signature line. Formerly known as the adidas KB8, the retro silhouette features a black tumbled leather upper with glossy patent leather three-stripes. An adidas tag in purple and gold adorns the tongue, while an embroidered '98' appears on the vamp, replacing the '8' on the original 1998 release. Angular lines define the lightweight EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Mad IIInfinity Black Carbon
results.story: The adidas Mad IIInfinity 'Black Carbon' debuts a retro-futuristic silhouette inspired by the Crazy 1. Secured with a concealed lacing system, the streamlined upper features breathable black mesh with a tonal synthetic suede mudguard. In addition to a gently curved line in metallic silver, the monochrome design is interrupted by adidas' three-stripes logo, finished in Lucid Blue at the vamp and back heel. The sneaker rides on a bulky EVA midsole with TPU inserts for improved stability.

results.name: Crazy 8 J '1998 All Star Game' 2024
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the 2024 edition of the adidas Crazy 8 J '1998 All Star Game' brings back Kobe Bryant's first All-Star shoe. Black tumbled leather is utilized on the upper, accented with tonal patent leather three-stripes and a purple and gold '98' embroidered on the vamp. An adidas Equipment tag decorates the tongue, while the retro Feet You Wear logo graces the medial collar. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a dynamic black and white EVA midsole, supported by adidas' Torsion System and a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

adidas Stan Smith Bape ABC Camo
results.story: The BAPE x adidas Stan Smith '30th Anniversary' celebrates three decades of the Japanese streetwear brand by bringing the iconic ABC Camo print to the classic sneaker. The distinctive all-over design, featuring an earthy blend of brown, tan and green hues, floods the leather upper, accented with perforated three-stripes. Dual branding appears on the tongue, while white leather back tabs display mismatched Trefoil and BAPE STA logos. 30th anniversary lace shines in a metallic gold finish. An off-white rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

results.name: Kader Sylla x Samba ADV 'Brown Gum'
results.story: Designed for the pro skateboarder hailing from Studio City, California, the Kader Sylla x adidas Samba ADV 'Brown Gum' is crafted from black tumbled leather with brown suede construction on the signature three-stripes, forefoot overlay and heel. 'KADER' is pressed into the lateral quarter panel in gold-foil lettering, matching the printed adidas Trefoil tag that adorns the tongue. A durable gum rubber cupsole sits low to the ground, offering enhanced traction and board feel.

results.name: adidas SC Premiere Kith Classics White Green (2019/2024)
results.story: KITH shows off its style with a June 2019 collaboration with adidas. Donning a white leather upper, the Kith x SC Premiere 'Green' features hits of grey suede on the toe box and tongue label for reinforcement. KITH chose Fairway Green for the heel counter, one of two colors unveiled as part of their Summer 2019 collection. An exaggerated rubber sole down below makes the shoe suitable for both athletic performance and streetwear style.

results.name: Wales Bonner x Samba 'Studded Pack - Cream'
results.story: Taken from the two-piece 'Studded Pack,' the Wales Bonner x adidas Samba 'Cream' features a full leather upper lined in satin. The shoe's iconic three-stripes are adorned with metallic studs, nodding to the signature motif of Wales Bonner's Fall/Winter 2023 apparel collection. Deco stitching surrounds the heel tab and fold-over tongue, while dual branding appears on the sockliner and woven tongue tag. Anchoring the timeless silhouette is a durable rubber cupsole.

results.name: Wales Bonner x Samba 'Studded Pack - Black'
results.story: Dropping as part of the 'Studded Pack,' the Wales Bonner x adidas Samba 'Black' reimagines the classic model with a premium build. The sleek silhouette carries a black leather upper, lined in satin and equipped with a low-cut padded collar. Metallic studs shine on the signature three-stripes, while white deco stitching outlines the back tab and fold-over tongue, featuring a co-branded woven label. The sneaker sits atop a low-profile rubber cupsole.

results.story: The adidas Predator Elite FT FG 'Solar Energy Pack' delivers a performance soccer cleat built for firm-ground surfaces. Equipped with a two-piece Primeknit collar, the durable black synthetic upper features Strikeskin grip elements for superior control. A fold-over tongue in Solar Red conceals the lace bed for improved durability and a sleek aesthetic. Anchoring the shoe is adidas' Controlframe outsole, which provides added stability and grip even at top speed.

results.story: The Travis Scott x Women's Air Jordan 1 Retro Low OG SP 'Canary' showcases the Houston rapper's signature reverse Swoosh, cropped and finished in Racer Blue adorning the lateral side of the shoe. A white leather upper is contrasted with yellow overlays at the forefoot and heel. A red and black Nike Air tag adorns the tongue, while mismatched Cactus Jack and Wings branding is embroidered on the heel tab of each shoe. The sneaker is underpinned by a traditional cupsole, highlighted by white textured sidewalls and a gum rubber outsole.

Wmns Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Latte'
results.story: The Women’s Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG ‘Latte’ dresses the classic silhouette in color blocking that mirrors the ‘Dark Mocha’ AJ1 from 2020. Built with a crisp white base, the leather upper features black accents on the forefoot overlay and Swoosh, along with contrasting hits of dark tan on the heel and collar flap. The latter is marked with the iconic Wings logo, while a woven Nike Air tag embellishes the tongue. Underpinning the high-top is a vintage off-white rubber midsole, fitted with an Air-sole heel unit encapsulated in a lightweight polyurethane wedge.

results.name: Wmns Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Georgia Peach'
results.story: The Women's Air Jordan 3 Retro 'Georgia Peach' showcases a white tumbled leather upper, contrasted by orange molded eyelets and fortified with grey elephant print overlays at the forefoot and heel. Jumpman branding adorns the tongue and back heel. A vintage off-white finish is applied to the polyurethane midsole, featuring visible Air-sole cushioning and a wraparound splash of Cosmic Clay.

results.name: Wmns Air Max DN 'White Metallic Silver'
results.story: The Nike Women's Air Max DN 'White Metallic Silver' showcases Nike's Dynamic Air unit system, which utilizes a dual-pressure, four-tubed Nike Air unit in the heel of the lightweight Phylon midsole. The innovative cushioning setup creates a reactive sensation with every step, as air flows freely between the tubes in each chamber. Up top, the seamless white textile build features a haptic overlay with a silicone finish, bringing a unique texture to the sleek silhouette.

results.name: Wmns Air Max 1 '86 OG 'Big Bubble - Royal'
results.story: The Nike Women’s Air Max 1 ‘86 OG ‘Big Bubble’ in ‘Royal’ features an original color scheme, paired with revised tooling inspired by the short-lived introductory run of the vintage running shoe. The upper combines ventilated white mesh with synthetic suede overlays in a pale grey finish. Royal blue accents settle on the molded eyelets, Swoosh, and suede mudguard. The sneaker rests on a white foam midsole, rendered in a classic wedge shape and fitted with a large-window Max Air unit in the heel.

results.name: Jordan 4 Retro Metallic Gold (Women's)
results.story: The Women’s Air Jordan 4 Retro ‘Metallic Gold’ delivers a pristine colorway of the legacy silhouette. A subtle off-white finish is executed on the smooth leather upper, featuring breathable quarter panel netting and metallic gold eyelets. Jumpman branding decorates the tongue and molded heel tab. A color-matched polyurethane midsole packs a visible Air-sole unit in the heel for lightweight cushioning. Underfoot, a cream-hued herringbone traction outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Sabrina 1 'Oregon Ducks'
results.story: The Nike Women’s Sabrina 1 ‘Oregon Ducks’ pays homage to Sabrina Ionescu’s alma mater. The shoe makes use of a mesh and textile upper in contrasting green and yellow hues. Sabrina’s personal logo appears on the tongue patch, while a Swoosh outlined in black embroidery adorns the lateral side panel. ‘QUACK’ is inscribed on the lateral sidewall in a playful nod to the Oregon Ducks. Performance benefits include a cushy React foam midsole with a top-loaded Zoom Air unit in the forefoot.

results.story: The Nike Women's Dunk Low 'Give Her Flowers' features an off-white leather upper, with plush textile overlays covered in an embossed floral print. The pristine design is interrupted by discreet pops of color: a molded rose pinned to the lateral heel and crimson Nike branding on the woven tongue tag. Inside the shoe, custom sockliners are inscribed with the phrase 'You deserve flowers.' The low-top rests on a rubber cupsole in a solid white finish.

results.name: Wmns Air Max 90 Futura 'Give Her Flowers'
results.story: The Nike Women's Air Max 90 Futura 'Give Her Flowers' features a plush white textile upper, covered in an embossed floral pattern and fortified with tonal leather overlays. A molded red rose emblem is pinned to the lateral heel, while 'Air Max' is embroidered on the tongue in crimson lettering. Webbing pull tabs are added to the tongue and heel for easy on and off. Inside the shoe, pink sockliners display an inscription that reads 'You Deserve Flowers.' The sneaker rides on a matching white foam midsole with a visible Max Air unit in the heel.

results.name: Wmns Air Max 1 '87 'Malachite'
results.story: The Nike Women’s Air Max 1 ‘87 ‘Malachite’ features an upper that combines breathable white mesh with grey synthetic suede overlays at the midfoot and heel. The latter displays Nike Air branding in green embroidery, matching the molded upper eyelets, signature Swoosh and suede mudguard. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a white polyurethane midsole, featuring a visible Air-sole unit in the heel.

results.name: Jordan 1 Retro High OG Dusted Clay (Women's)
results.story: The Women's Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Dusted Clay' dons a supple suede upper, featuring a light tan base with brown forefoot overlays and a color-matched Swoosh. A contrasting burnt orange hue lands on the heel and collar flap, marked with a debossed Wings logo on the lateral side. A vintage off-white finish is applied to the midsole, fitted with Air-sole cushioning in the heel and supported by a grippy orange rubber outsole.
